      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.4/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/31853864-5f40-11e3-b74d-52540035b04c).  Ran 14 tests.  2 tests failed: lustre-rsync-test, conf-sanity.",
